<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="365" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,151,968]" pageId="3" pageNumber="365">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,872,896]" pageId="3" pageNumber="365">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[619,873,872,896]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Xenovarta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="365" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longicornis">
<emphasis box="[619,873,872,896]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="365">Xenovarta longicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but can be distinguished by the underdeveloped subapical lobe of the style (
<figureCitation box="[458,521,908,932]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,249,1759,1782]" captionTargetBox="[214,1374,579,1705]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[188,1398,566,1738]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Xenovarta lui sp. n. A: male pygofer side, lateral view; B: valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D: connective, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus, ventral and lateral view, respectively." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/216754/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="365">
Fig. 
<number box="[511,521,908,932]" pageId="3" pageNumber="365" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
C) and by the aedeagus with a pair of subapical processes (
<figureCitation box="[1185,1252,908,932]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,249,1759,1782]" captionTargetBox="[214,1374,579,1705]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[188,1398,566,1738]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Xenovarta lui sp. n. A: male pygofer side, lateral view; B: valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D: connective, dorsal view; E &amp; F: aedeagus, ventral and lateral view, respectively." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/216754/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="365">
Figs 
<number box="[1241,1252,908,932]" pageId="3" pageNumber="365" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
E, 
<number box="[1287,1298,908,932]" pageId="3" pageNumber="365" value="1.0">1</number>
F).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
